author: bmwlego
title: Gift From a Student I'll Never Forget
review: My student Kayto and his family gave me this key chain as a gift last year. I love it. It is attached to my keys and I see it every day to remind me of my love of LEGO! The LEGO logo on the wizard's back is scratching off and his legs are very loose after using it for half a year but it is standing up pretty well otherwise. These minifig key chains are great. I can see wanting to collect them but I have to limit what LEGO I collect due to space restraints.
